comments: Robinson (MIA) and Bogdanovic (SAC) engage and disengage off-ball.
Hield (SAC) briefly has his hands on Robinson's (MIA) hips and quickly releases as he moves to set the pick.
Bogdanovic (SAC) makes marginal contact with Robinson (MIA) and does not affect his ability to gain control of the hand-off.
Adebayo (MIA) initiates contact with Bagley III's (SAC) left arm during the put-back attempt.
Johnson (MIA) moves into Fox's (SAC) space and makes some contact with Fox's backside/right arm as the screen is set, but it is marginal.
Hield (SAC) and Robinson (MIA) engage and disengage off-ball.
Bogdanovic (SAC) and Dragic (MIA) engage and disengage off-ball.
Barnes (SAC) extends two hands to Dragic's (MIA) body and affects his FOM as he cuts through the lane.
Robinson (MIA) makes marginal contact with Fox's (SAC) side after his gather. Adebayo (MIA) then cleanly blocks Fox's driving shot attempt before incidental contact is made thereafter.
Adebayo (MIA) makes marginal contact with Bagley III's (SAC) left arm after Bagley III has already lost control of the ball during rebounding.
Johnson (MIA) extends his arms forward and initiates contact with Bagley III's (SAC) left forearm during his upward shooting motion.
Fox's (SAC) left foot touches the line, but does not cross it. Fox remains out of bounds.
Bjelica (SAC) and Johnson (MIA) engage and disengage with one another during rebounding.
Adebayo (MIA) firms up in his screening position in Fox's (SAC) path and does not deliver the contact.
Dragic (MIA) makes marginal contact with Bjelica's (SAC) front during his drive toward the lane.
Bjelica (SAC) makes some contact with his off-arm around Dragic's (MIA) midsection, but it is marginal.
Bjelica (SAC) releases the shot attempt prior to the expiration of the shot clock.
Dragic (MIA) makes marginal contact with Bjelica's (SAC) front during his upward shooting motion.
Johnson (MIA) makes marginal contact with Bjelica's (SAC) side during his upward shooting motion.
Adebayo (MIA) releases from the contact with Joseph (SAC) near the basket.
Fox (SAC) makes marginal contact with Nunn (MIA) after his release and doesn't affect his ability to follow-through naturally following the jump shot attempt.
Fox (SAC) legally keeps his hand on the side of the ball prior to driving toward the lane.
Adebayo (MIA) establishes himself in a screening position in Fox's (SAC) path and does not deliver the contact.
Adebayo (MIA) makes marginal contact with Hield's (SAC) backside as he begins to roll out of his screening position.
Adebayo (MIA) and Bagley III (SAC) engage and disengage with one another during the rebound.
Adebayo (MIA) makes marginal contact with Bagley III's (SAC) front during the inbound.
Bogdanovic (SAC) and Dragic (MIA) engage and disengage with one another along the lane line.
Bagley III (SAC) makes marginal contact with Dragic's (MIA) front during his drive into the lane.
Johnson (MIA) makes marginal contact with Bjelica's (SAC) side/front during his drive toward the lane.
Fox (SAC) makes marginal body contact with Dragic (MIA) near half-court.
Johnson (MIA) makes marginal contact with Fox's (SAC) side as he begins to roll out of his screening position.
Bjelica (SAC) makes marginal body contact with Dragic (MIA) after his gather.
Adebayo (MIA) cleanly strips Bjelica (SAC) of the ball after he secures the rebound.
Dragic (MIA) briefly grasps and then quickly releases Bjelica's (SAC) left arm during rebounding.
Bagley III (SAC) delivers contact to Leonard's (MIA) backside that dislodges him from position during rebounding.
Dragic (MIA) and Fox (SAC) engage and disengage during the inbound.
Joseph (SAC) briefly has his arms around Dragic's (MIA) midsection before correcting.
Nunn (MIA) establishes himself in the front-court prior to receiving the pass.
Bogdanovic (SAC) commits the take foul on Nunn (MIA).

call_type: Turnover: Lost Ball Out of Bounds
comments: Fox (SAC) touches the ball last before it goes out of bounds.
Hield (SAC) wraps Dragic's (MIA) midsection with both arms, affecting his FOM during the inbound.
Johnson (MIA) legally contests Bogdanovic's (SAC) jump shot attempt and cleanly blocks it.
Bjelica (SAC) commits the take foul on Nunn (MIA).
